entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have gained Jak Chucka's trust and respect.  Now you may be able to get that Gungan record bauble decrypted for Broma Lak.
entries.journal_entry_description: Broma Lak directed you to a Gungan informant named Jak Chucka.  Before Jak will decrypt the Gungan record bauble, he wants some...problems taken care of.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The nesting kaadu atop the hill makes too much noise for Jak to conduct business.  Thin the herd.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have completed you end of the contract. Return to Jak Chucka so he can fulfill his.
